{"tid":1519414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[前線後勤支援] 其實用無線電發放即時情報有無得諗？","createTime":"2019-08-30T14:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T14:43:47.000Z","uid":229411,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0030a63b724d871a83b5c3bf6ac93dcd3dfbc612","tid":1519414,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"出現大型示威活動時候，淨係會讀該區嘅情報，資訊主要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由 TG Channel Scott Scout認證哨兵消息提供</span></span>。如果喺接收範圍內<span style=\"color: red;\">可以要求特別情報資訊</span>，例如確保撤退路線安全，現場情報fact check等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就可以確保到唔會有<span style=\"color: orange;\">fake news</span>令前線散水，甚至陷入困境。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為尊重前線嘅決定權，無線電支援<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會主動提供任何戰術上資訊</span>，除非收到救助。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家俾吓意見，提點吓有無安全顧慮，同埋實際上運作方法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2da9916749379ae11707e827c0436f92545b73","tid":1519414,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0vGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=91cba4fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span 